title: 21 Savage Returns For Sneaker Shopping With Complex
author: Complex
description:
21 Savage returns to Complex's Sneaker Shopping and joins Joe La Puma at Wish in Atlanta to talk about his love for rare Air Jordans, how his collection stacks up to Lil Yachty's, and how Nike didn't send him the sneaker they made for him.
